body:
I can confirm it works like described in https://github.com/yiisoft/yii2/issues/20300#issuecomment-2565243249 and `clearstatcache()` fixes this problem.

```php
var_dump(Yii::$app->cache->get('__METHOD__'));
Yii::$app->cache->set('__METHOD__', 'test2', 10);
var_dump(Yii::$app->cache->get('__METHOD__'));
Yii::$app->cache->set('__METHOD__', 'test3', 10);
clearstatcache();
var_dump(Yii::$app->cache->get('__METHOD__'));
```

result:

```
bool(false)
bool(false)
string(5) "test3"
```
